    public interface LibraryContainerA
extends OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Container A'. A library holds the definitions of all important basic elements used in the architecture model as for instance function types, device types, or resource types.

    The following features are supported:

    • Data Types
    • Resource Types
    • Resource Bundles
    • Resource Modifiers
    • Resource Type Dissimilarities
    • Task Types
    • Task Type Dissimilarity
    • Signal Types
    • Device Types
    • Device Type Symmetries
    • Device Type Dissimilarities
    • Connection Types
    • Wire Types
